# FastAPI

> Modern, high-performance Python web framework for building APIs with automatic documentation.

---

## Overview

FastAPI is a modern Python framework that provides:
- **Performance**: One of the fastest Python frameworks (Starlette + Pydantic)
- **Type Safety**: Pydantic models for validation and serialization
- **Auto Documentation**: OpenAPI (Swagger) and ReDoc out of the box
- **Async Support**: Native async/await support
- **Standards Based**: OpenAPI, JSON Schema, OAuth2

---

## Why FastAPI

| vs Flask | vs Django REST |
|----------|----------------|
| Native async | Simpler setup |
| Auto validation | Better performance |
| Type hints | Modern Python |
| Auto docs | Less boilerplate |

### Performance Comparison

| Framework | Requests/sec |
|-----------|--------------|
| FastAPI | ~15,000 |
| Flask | ~4,000 |
| Django | ~3,000 |

